@startuml

actor User
participant "Angular\nFrontend" as FE
participant "Auth\nInterceptor" as INT
participant "Elysia\nREST API" as API
participant "Auth Guard" as GUARD
participant "Prisma ORM" as ORM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Register ==
User -> FE: Formular ausfüllen
FE -> INT: POST /api/auth/register
INT -> API: (kein Token nötig)
API -> ORM: user.create(hash(password))
ORM -> DB: INSERT INTO "User"
DB --> ORM: user
ORM --> API: ok
API --> FE: 201 Created
FE --> User: "Registrierung erfolgreich"

== Login ==
User -> FE: Credentials eingeben
FE -> INT: POST /api/auth/login
INT -> API: { username, email, password }
API -> ORM: user.findUnique(email)
ORM -> DB: SELECT FROM "User"
DB --> ORM: user
ORM --> API: user
API -> API: verifyPassword(hash, password)
API -> API: createAccessToken (15min)
API -> API: createRefreshToken (7d)
API --> FE: { accessToken, userId }\n+ Set-Cookie: refresh_token (HttpOnly)
FE -> FE: Token im Memory speichern
FE --> User: Weiterleitung zu /home

== GET /api/todos (mit Auth) ==
User -> FE: Homepage öffnen
FE -> INT: GET /api/todos
INT -> INT: Bearer Token anhängen
INT -> API: GET /api/todos\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD -> GUARD: verifyAccessToken → userId
GUARD --> API: { userId }
API -> ORM: todo.findMany({ userId })
ORM -> DB: SELECT FROM "Todo" WHERE userId
DB --> ORM: todos[]
ORM --> API: todos[]
API --> FE: todos[]
FE --> User: Todo-Liste rendern

== POST /api/todos ==
User -> FE: Neues Todo erstellen
FE -> INT: POST /api/todos { title, description }
INT -> API: + Bearer Token
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD --> API: { userId }
API -> ORM: todo.create({ ...body, userId })
ORM -> DB: INSERT INTO "Todo"
DB --> ORM: todo
ORM --> API: ok
API --> FE: 201 Created
FE -> FE: refreshTodos()

== PATCH /api/todos/:id ==
User -> FE: Todo bearbeiten
FE -> INT: PATCH /api/todos/:id { title, description }
INT -> API: + Bearer Token
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD --> API: { userId }
API -> ORM: todo.update({ id, userId })
ORM -> DB: UPDATE "Todo" WHERE id AND userId
DB --> ORM: updated
ORM --> API: ok
API --> FE: ok
FE -> FE: refreshTodos()

== DELETE /api/todos/:id ==
User -> FE: Todo löschen
FE -> INT: DELETE /api/todos/:id
INT -> API: + Bearer Token
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD --> API: { userId }
API -> ORM: todo.delete({ id, userId })
ORM -> DB: DELETE FROM "Todo" WHERE id AND userId
DB --> ORM: ok
API --> FE: ok
FE -> FE: refreshTodos()

== DELETE /api/todos ==
User -> FE: Alle Todos löschen
FE -> INT: DELETE /api/todos
INT -> API: + Bearer Token
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD --> API: { userId }
API -> ORM: todo.deleteMany({ userId })
ORM -> DB: DELETE FROM "Todo" WHERE userId
DB --> ORM: ok
API --> FE: ok
FE -> FE: refreshTodos()

== Token Refresh (automatisch bei 401) ==
FE -> INT: beliebiger API-Request
INT -> API: + Bearer Token (abgelaufen)
API -> GUARD: Token verifizieren
GUARD --> API: 401 Unauthorized
API --> INT: 401
INT -> API: POST /api/auth/refresh\n+ Cookie: refresh_token
API -> API: verifyRefreshToken
API -> API: neues Token-Paar erstellen
API --> INT: { accessToken }\n+ Set-Cookie: refresh_token (rotiert)
INT -> INT: Token im Memory aktualisieren
INT -> API: Original-Request wiederholen\n+ neuer Bearer Token
API --> FE: ursprüngliche Antwort

== Logout ==
User -> FE: Logout klicken
FE -> INT: POST /api/auth/logout
INT -> API: + Cookie
API -> API: clearRefreshCookie
API --> FE: Set-Cookie: refresh_token (Max-Age=0)
FE -> FE: Token aus Memory löschen
FE --> User: Weiterleitung zu /login

@enduml